
  Medicham    Fighting Type Pokémon

  It is said that through meditation, 
  MEDICHAM heightens energy inside 
  its body and sharpens its sixth 
  sense.  Medicham hides its 
  presence by merging itself with 
  fields and mountains. 
	Evolution Chain
